{"tid":2041373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實黎到呢一步都係源於銅鑼灣書店一本書","createTime":"2020-05-29T07:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T08:17:18.000Z","uid":173357,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6df0186238ca398027a13b09752d8f34c050d122","tid":2041373,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"一本鳩作既書令到維尼震怒要國安捉走成間書店啲員工，林榮基爆晒成單野出黎又令到維尼推出逃犯條例。終於黎到今日呢個地步！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本書名好似叫做《維尼和他5個女人》，有冇巴打睇過本書講咩同埋出自邊條友手筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：想買"},{"pid":"b9343318ced848814f73445079302fef866eb48f","tid":2041373,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:58:26.000Z","msg":"刁總畀人屌屎眼果本？"},{"pid":"3d4b717c4493a067135f8e1292e2f74c5c099b2c","tid":2041373,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"溥儀和他的五個女人"},{"pid":"e3c7a39f47a74148989fc4706c84fb7f29590866","tid":2041373,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82771fadc20e95049a7e290caafa2c88e670a232","tid":2041373,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣書店股東及員工失蹤事件的當事人之一林榮基在接受《蘋果日報》的訪問中表示，他遭扣押期間接觸過執行及策劃的中央專案組高層人員，但未見過王立強。王所說的銅鑼灣書店行動沒有提及細節，「應該是聽來的！」，並且<strong>王提及書店計劃出版中共總書記習近平與女人的書籍，與他了解的事實也有所落差。</strong>"},{"pid":"4102c7f56b4525adab201d31bc0ab14915243740","tid":2041373,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"睇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有講佢初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e2028b7d3db4d3e037f79c44fdbf10865a9d4f","tid":2041373,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4b717c4493a067135f8e1292e2f74c5c099b2c","tid"